No. 537,

Misc.

Rinaldi v. Yeager, Warden, et al. Donald A. Robinson for appellant. Arthur J. Sills, Attorney General of New Jersey, and Eugene T. Urbaniak, Deputy Attorney General, for appellees.

Appeal from D. C. N. J. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Probable jurisdiction noted. The case is transferred to the appellate docket.
